OL,6,FITV News' Olivia Guthrie reports on
OL,7,Fthe latest Met Police racism row
OL,9,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak is said to
OL,10,Fbe "appalled" by an exchange at a pro-
OL,11,FPalestinian protest in which a
OL,12,FMetropolitan Police officer threatened
OL,13,Fa man with arrest and told him he was
OL,14,F"openly Jewish".
OL,16,FGideon Falter is an anti-semitism
OL,17,Fcampaigner who was close to a pro-
OL,18,FPalestinian march last weekend when a
OL,19,Fpolice officer stopped him and made
OL,20,Fthe remark on 13 April.
