OL,6,FWhile Government sources have
OL,7,Fexpressed condemnation of the incident
OL,8,Finvolving Mr Falter, they have been
OL,9,Fkeen to stress that nobody in
OL,10,FGovernment is threatening Sir Mark's
OL,11,Fposition.
OL,13,FOne source said: "The PM has seen the
OL,14,Ffootage and is as appalled as everyone
OL,15,Felse by the officer calling Mr Falter
OL,16,F'openly Jewish'.
