OL,6,F"He expects the Met Commissioner to
OL,7,Faccount for how it happened and what
OL,8,Fhe will do to ensure officers do more
OL,9,Fto make Jewish communities in London
OL,10,Ffeel safe ` and Sadiq Khan to do his
OL,11,Fjob in holding the Met to account."
OL,13,FThe mayor of London Sadiq Khan has
OL,14,Falso summoned the Metropolitan Police
OL,15,FCommissioner to discuss "community
OL,16,Frelations", after a row about the
OL,17,Fforce's handling of the protest. They
OL,18,Fare set to meet on Monday.
