OL,6,FThe Commissioner is also expected to
OL,7,Fmeet the Home Secretary, James
OL,8,FCleverly, in the coming days, and has
OL,9,Fcome under pressure to resign after a
OL,10,Fseries of criticisms of the Met's
OL,11,Fapproach to protests over the past six
OL,12,Fmonths.
OL,14,FHowever, Government sources have
OL,15,Fplayed down the possibility that Sir
OL,16,FMark could be sacked and he is
OL,17,Funderstood to retain the confidence of
OL,18,Fthe mayor.
