OL,6,FBoth the Mayor and the Home Secretary
OL,7,Fhave responsibility for holding the
OL,8,Fcommissioner to account, although the
OL,9,Fmayor is the one tasked with setting
OL,10,Fthe strategic direction for policing
OL,11,Fin London.
OL,13,FA spokesman for Mr Khan said the Met's
OL,14,Fhandling of the incident was
OL,15,F"concerning" and its initial statement
OL,16,Fhad been "insensitive and wrong".
OL,18,FThe spokesman added: "The Met have an
OL,19,Fextremely difficult job ` particularly
OL,20,Fso when it comes to operational
OL,21,Fdecisions taken while policing marches.
