OL,6,F"But in the end the Met must have the
OL,7,Fconfidence of the communities they
OL,8,Fserve and it is right that they have
OL,9,Fapologised for the way the incident
OL,10,Fwas handled and their original public
OL,11,Fresponse."
OL,13,FSir Mark said: "Every member of the
OL,14,FMet is determined to ensure that
OL,15,FLondon is a city in which everyone
OL,16,Ffeels safe.
OL,18,F"We absolutely understand how
OL,19,Fvulnerable Jewish and Muslim Londoners
OL,20,Ffeel since the terrorist attacks on
OL,21,FIsrael.
